# imigrai backend bootstrap

Bootstrap do backend FastAPI para o SaaS de imigracao.

## Stack

- Python 3.12+
- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy 2 (async)
- Alembic
- PostgreSQL
- Redis
- Celery + Celery Beat
- uv
- Docker Compose

## Estrutura principal

- `app/api`: roteadores HTTP (health + v1)
- `app/core`: config, seguranca, observabilidade
- `app/db`: base, sessao e migracoes
- `apps/*`: dominios modulares

## Subir local com Docker

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

Endpoints:

- `GET /health/live`
- `GET /health/ready`
- `POST /api/v1/auth/register`
- `POST /api/v1/auth/login`
- `POST /api/v1/auth/refresh`
- `GET /api/v1/auth/me`
- `GET /openapi.json`
- `GET /docs`
- `GET /redoc`

## Migrações

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

## Qualidade

```bash
uv pip install -e .[dev]
ruff check .
black --check .
pytest
pre-commit install
```
